Place the script execuatble in your bin directory in order to access it anywhere in the system.

Example usage:

user/home/dir$ 
user/home/dir$ 
user/home/dir$ ls
exampledoc.tex
user/home/dir$ texit exampledoc
Input: exampledoc
Opening: exampledoc.pdf
Texing: exampledoc.tex
File size:  2679
Compile success at Fri Mar 6 12:09:06 PST 2020
Compiles: 1
